dji.sdk.api.Camera

Class DJICameraPlaybackState

  • java.lang.Object
    • dji.sdk.api.Camera.DJICameraPlaybackState

  • public class DJICameraPlaybackState
extends java.lang.Object

    DJI Camera Playback State Class

    This class will hold the information from play back state.This data structure will be used in the callback of DJICameraPlayBackStateCallBack. The CameraPlaybackMode here will provide notification of which kind of work camera currently doing, such as deleting imagine(s). The CameraMediaFileType includes type of JPEG, DNG and Video. The remains will provide information of play back mode. For example, numbersOfThumbnail means the number of thumbnail in current play back page.
    Version:
    V2.4.0
    Author:
    DJI Software
